Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We asked Dr. Wakaouji to be Full Moon's producer, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.81,0:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...for some reason, he wouldn't accept the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:05.36,Notice 1 (Ep.25) - Modified,,0,0,0,Sign,{\move(322.003,119,323.004,110,23,899)}{\r\t(0,2184,\fscx175\fscy150\blur0.6)}Producer's Chair
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I tried all sorts of things, but to no avail.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We were ready to give up on Dr. Wakaouji...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or, so we thought...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.44,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But then, he suddenly said that he would be the producer!!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like something Takuto said made him come to that decision.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But I wonder what is was that he said?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Meroko,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Meroko,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.50,Meroko,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.09,Takuto,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.09,0:00:29.73,Meroko,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's Shii-chan's {\i1}Music Power{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.56,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hi!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Covering for Shii today... Oda Shizuo!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.31,0:00:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is everyone feeling great?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now then, let's go straight to this week's top news!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.52,Notice 1 (Ep.26),,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.6\pos(152,313)}Full Moon's pro ducer
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.52,Notice 1 (Ep.26),,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.6\pos(276,330)}is someone from  the past!?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.52,0:00:54.49,Notice 1 (Ep.26) v2,,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.5\fs21\frx358\fry0\c&HFDFBF8&\3c&H3B372F&\pos(197,390)}Full Moon's producer
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.52,0:00:54.49,Notice 1 (Ep.26) v2,,0,0,0,Sign,{\blur0.5\fs21\frx358\fry0\c&HFDFBF8&\3c&H3B372F&\pos(380,415)}is someone from the past?!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an8\be1}It seems that the former Prince of Route L... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.86,0:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an8\be1}...is making a comeback to the music scene as Full Moon's producer. {}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well done, Ooshige-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I never thought that you'd net that Wakaouji-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, let's both do out best.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And what's more, the song is one that everyone knows!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:07.42,0:01:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Route L's mystical and famous song...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a cover of {\i1}Eternal Snow{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In fact, regarding this song...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.42,0:01:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Takasu Kouhei is also planning on releasing this song with the new artist Wakamatsu Madoka.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.02,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How intriguing, it looks like the arrival of a powerful rival for Takasu Kouhei.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For pop singers back in the sixties...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there were often problems where different singers would sing the same song,
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}but nowadays, we almost never see that happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why this is such a hot topic.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's late.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, he's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.25,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Those clothes...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-They don't suit me, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.09,0:02:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order to rediscover my feelings,\NI decided to try this out.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.15,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, they totally fit you!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You look cool!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.77,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.69,0:02:13.65,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,345)\bord2.5}What I Want to Say...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah, this is Takasu.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How's it going?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um, it'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By okay, you mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...whether or not you'll win?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You want to win.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why you called me, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, get that look off your face.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have faith in me!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, yes, that's the look.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's the face of Wakamatsu Madoka.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.07,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're already done?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That was fast.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, no, that's great.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Send it my way then.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You've already sent it?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're fast, Kumi-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Delivered as promised.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.95,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't lose. {}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.83,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way I can lose.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-You haven't decided?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's not a good thing, is it...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even under these circumstances...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.72,0:03:30.48,Notice 2 (Ep.26),,0,0,0,Sign,{\move(155,140,480,140,42,9828)}Full Moon's Second Single Concept Meeting {continuous pan, w00t, perfect pan}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't think that planning ahead is what's important here.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Coming up with something that everyone agrees with...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that's what our job is.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even if you say that, our schedule is...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If we went through a superficial routine to arrange a song...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and only worried about the schedule, I'm not sure how things would work out.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Superficial?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can do something about the schedule.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But if we don't decide on a concept...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Without that, we can't decide whom to ask to arrange it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We won't be able to decide which staff members to use either...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why, by all means...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we'd like you to decide as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}, through this song...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...what's the number one thing that you want to say to your fans?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To my fans?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't need to be specific.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't have to answer right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Spend some time thinking about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll give you plenty of time.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Okay...
