Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's it for today.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See ya.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm worried now...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure, he may have talent...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but can he really do something like this?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have faith in that doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A... w-well...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You looked like you were fretting over something...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.94,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've been only thinking about what I wanted to say to Eichi-kun this whole time.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I never realized it until it was mentioned, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What I want to say with this song...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just what is it...?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what it was.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm... what you want to say, huh?
