Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eternal... {\alpha&Hff&}Eternal... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eternal... Eternal... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Edamame?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course that's not it!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.14,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What that doctor was saying wasn't about understanding the lyrics.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's something much simpler.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here's an example.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's say someone hears you sing {\i1}Eternal Snow{\i0}...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Will they burst into tears?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or will it give them courage?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or will it force them to smile?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Or will it make them unable to hold in their laughter?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.71,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're overdoing it.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what he meant.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How about it?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, try thinking it out carefully.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have you found an answer?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nope...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You didn't stay up again, did you?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I slept enough.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But I woke up because something was bothering me.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is bothering you?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.07,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What were my father's feelings when he wrote this song?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.16,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right, what kind of a person was your father?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I dunno...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not just my father...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nothing about my mother, either...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though they're your parents?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The story that the teacher at the orphanage told me was that...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...my mother died right after giving birth to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When I was one, my father...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...became a star in the sky...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After that...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she also told me that my father was a musician.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, I started listening to the songs he wrote.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then, two years ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.28,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be living with you from now on!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When Grandma took me in...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I tried asking her about it, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's nothing to say.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.75,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Grandma...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It seems like she hates talking about my mother and father.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Up to this every day, I haven't learned anything.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In that case, let's try asking that doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'Cause...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...he was in the same band as your father, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's good!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's try that, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You might discover some hints.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I only knew the two of them while they were in the band.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.16,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your mother, Hazuki-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...always helped out where she could.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In age...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she was younger, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she was like an older sister.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A very kind person.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, one day...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I learned that Hazuki-san was pregnant...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're going to elope?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're about to go on tour!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you, the leader, disappear...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aoi-san?!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was pregnant with me, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.03,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...your grandmother was against their marriage.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Our leader, your father...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Aoi-san disappeared...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and Route L was forced to break up.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After that...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I had no idea what happened to Aoi-san and Hazuki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But then, two years ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.01,0:09:42.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}N-Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm Kouyama Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please take good care of me!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought that you looked like Hazuki-san, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I never suspected that it was true.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course, when I was around your grandmother, I never said a word.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Father... Mother... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did you find any hints?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... yes. Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Could it be that...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...my father wrote that song for my mother?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Could be.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to know more!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}More about my father and mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe there's a memento or something that they left behind?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go look!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If we look around the house...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there might be something.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think there is?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're talking about your grandma here.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She might have thrown it all out.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We won't know that until we look.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.28,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If there is something, then is should be {\i1}there{\i0} ...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...in the shed!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.30,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}Madoka can't answer the phone right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\an8}Please leave a message after the tone.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}Hi!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}Madoka?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}It's me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}You've been so distant lately.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}Let's play together like we used to!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}Acting this seriously...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\fscx90\fscy90}It's not like you.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't lose to someone like you!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I might have come a little too early.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morni...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.76,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He was up all night...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.77,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Up until now...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.60,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the people of this world...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.56,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone has been cold to me.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.44,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is the first time...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.87,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.03,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.08,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In order to live up to your expectations...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.96,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's an old issue of Ribon!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My mother read Ribon too, huh...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I feel so close...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Lemme see. Lemme see.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look at this, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is hilarious!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you think we're playing around here?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A mouse!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a mouse!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a mouse!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over here!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This mouse is...!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.39,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This looks relatively new.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look out!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The box is the only thing here that looks particularly new.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Open it up and take a look inside.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, you... that was dangerous!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was so scared!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just from that...?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... me?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This isn't me...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is... my mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She looks just like you.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A jeweled music box, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is it broken?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Hey...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To Hazuki, with love...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So this is from my father?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Most likely.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The music box my father gave my mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're inside of here...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My father's...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...feelings for my mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to hear them...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My father's feelings...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a good song.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Warm...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This warm feeling...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How can I describe it...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.59,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... I can't put it into words...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, that's your phone.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... a job suddenly came up.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you come out now?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be outside, then.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A job suddenly came up.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.15,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll stay at home.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}C-Crap, she's found us!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did she find out...?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.79,0:18:33.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm pregnant with that man's child.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That man's child...?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you won't accept it...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll leave this house!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With a body as weak as yours...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you give birth to a child...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hazuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Music...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I hate music...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.37,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Always... taking away everything important to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It was a present from my father to my mother.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've found out what I want to say.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}I want to make people feel warm inside with my music.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}I even want people who hate music...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}...fall in love with music.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.92,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.08,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Father... {\alpha&Hff&}Mother... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.63,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Father... Mother... {}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto! We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  and Dr. Wakaouji...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A magazine says that they're having a steamy love affair! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That can't possibly be true!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How did that happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's gotta be the work of Wakamatsu Madoka again!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.57,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even up to the bitter end... that girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}One problem down, and another pops up, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate, we'll never get to the recording!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I Will not Lose
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.34,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look forward to it.
