Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:50.16,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:56.63,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:27.74,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.96,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.50,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:44.01,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:50.47,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.23,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:00.86,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
